---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Mire">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-indigo max-w-none text-gray-600">
      <p class="mb-4">Last updated: March 8, 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing and using Mire ("the Service"), you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. Research Submission</h2>
      <p>Users who submit research papers ("Contributors") represent and warrant that:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>They own or have the necessary licenses, rights, consents, and permissions to publish the content.</li>
        <li>The content does not plagiarize or infringe upon the rights of any third party.</li>
        <li>The content is accurate and does not contain hate speech, harassment, or illegal material.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>Contributors retain full ownership of their submitted research. By submitting content to Mire, you grant us a worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free license to use, reproduce, distribute, and display the content in connection with the Service.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Content Integrity</h2>
      <p>As an archival platform for student research, we maintain a policy of content permanence. Once published, articles cannot be modified or deleted except in cases of:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li>Proven copyright infringement or plagiarism.</li>
        <li>Serious ethical violations or hate speech.</li>
        <li>Privacy breaches exposing sensitive personal information.</li>
        <li>Legal orders from competent authorities.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>The Service is provided "as is". Mire makes no warranties, expressed or implied, regarding the accuracy or reliability of any research content hosted on the platform.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
